    <rigor-reason>Wrapper supports ALL 5 modes (compose/view/reply/forward/draft) — mode dispatch logic + URL-driven mode resolution is non-trivial; consumed by Wave 2 Code Page; touches the full mode matrix. FULL appropriate.</rigor-reason>
