  <notes>
    Wave 2 task 033 mounts this in the Code Page. Mode-specific pre-fill logic (e.g., `subject = 'Re: ' + original.subject`) lives in `modes/replyMode.ts` etc. (tasks 024-027) — wrapper just loads the source record + passes it through. Engine consumes `sourceRecord` and dispatches mode-specific initial-state derivation.

    `IComposerSourceRecord` deliberately mirrors `EmailComposerState` shape — the mode loaders (024-027) can copy fields directly when pre-filling.
  </notes>

